OL,6,GOn Saturday morning, Studio B in
OL,7,GBelfast was the base for TV coverage
OL,8,Gof the local elections in Northern
OL,9,GIreland, with Mark Carruthers
OL,10,Ganchoring.
OL,12,FThere were live link-ups with
OL,13,Freporters at the various count
OL,14,Fcentres across Northern Ireland.
OL,15,F Studio presentation included the use
OL,16,Fof a green-screen area for results
OL,17,Fgraphics.
OL,3,CBBC Election Northern Ireland 2023
